{"data":[{"name":"81:1","price":"当太阳暗淡的时候，","arabic":"إِذَا ٱلشَّمۡسُ كُوِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5801,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"81:2","price":"当星宿零落的时候，","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلنُّجُومُ ٱنكَدَرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5802,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"81:3","price":"当山峦崩溃的时候，","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجِبَالُ سُيِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5803,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"81:4","price":"当孕驼被抛弃的时候，","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡعِشَارُ عُطِّلَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5804,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"81:5","price":"当野兽被集合的时候，","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡوُحُوشُ حُشِرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5805,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"81:6","price":"当海洋澎湃的时候，","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡبِحَارُ سُجِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5806,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"81:7","price":"当灵魂被配合的时候，","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلنُّفُوسُ زُوِّجَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5807,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"81:8","price":"当被活埋的女孩被询问的时候：","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡمَوۡءُۥدَةُ سُئِلَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5808,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"81:9","price":"她为什么罪过而遭杀害呢？","arabic":"بِأَيِّ ذَنۢبٖ قُتِلَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5809,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"81:10","price":"当功过薄被展开的时候，","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلصُّحُفُ نُشِرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5810,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"81:11","price":"当天皮被揭去的时候，","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ كُشِطَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5811,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"81:12","price":"当火狱被燃着的时候，","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجَحِيمُ سُعِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5812,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"81:13","price":"当乐园被送近的时候，","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجَنَّةُ أُزۡلِفَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5813,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"81:14","price":"每个人都知道他所作过的善恶。","arabic":"عَلِمَتۡ نَفۡسٞ مَّآ أَحۡضَرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5814,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"81:15","price":"我誓以运行的众星--","arabic":"فَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِٱلۡخُنَّسِ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5815,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"81:16","price":"没落的行星，","arabic":"ٱلۡجَوَارِ ٱلۡكُنَّسِ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5816,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"81:17","price":"和逝去时的黑夜，","arabic":"وَٱلَّيۡلِ إِذَا عَسۡعَسَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5817,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"81:18","price":"照耀时的早晨，","arabic":"وَٱلصُّبۡحِ إِذَا تَنَفَّسَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5818,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"81:19","price":"这确是一个尊贵的使者的言辞，","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ لَقَوۡلُ رَسُولٖ كَرِيمٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5819,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"81:20","price":"他在宝座的主那里，是有权力的，是有地位的，","arabic":"ذِي قُوَّةٍ عِندَ ذِي ٱلۡعَرۡشِ مَكِينٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5820,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"81:21","price":"是众望所归，而且忠於职守的。","arabic":"مُّطَاعٖ ثَمَّ أَمِينٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5821,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"81:22","price":"你们的朋友，不是一个疯人，","arabic":"وَمَا صَاحِبُكُم بِمَجۡنُونٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5822,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"81:23","price":"他确已看见那个天使在明显的天边，","arabic":"وَلَقَدۡ رَءَاهُ بِٱلۡأُفُقِ ٱلۡمُبِينِ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5823,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"81:24","price":"他对幽玄不是吝教的。","arabic":"وَمَا هُوَ عَلَى ٱلۡغَيۡبِ بِضَنِينٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5824,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"81:25","price":"这不是被放逐的恶魔的言辞，","arabic":"وَمَا هُوَ بِقَوۡلِ شَيۡطَٰنٖ رَّجِيمٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5825,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"81:26","price":"你们将往哪里去呢？","arabic":"فَأَيۡنَ تَذۡهَبُونَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5826,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"81:27","price":"这只是对于众世界的教诲——","arabic":"إِنۡ هُوَ إِلَّا ذِكۡرٞ لِّلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5827,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"81:28","price":"对於你们中欲循规蹈矩者的教诲，","arabic":"لِمَن شَآءَ مِنكُمۡ أَن يَسۡتَقِيمَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5828,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"81:29","price":"你们不欲循规蹈矩，除非安拉——众世界的主——意欲的时候。","arabic":"وَمَا تَشَآءُونَ إِلَّآ أَن يَشَآءَ ٱللَّهُ رَبُّ ٱلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5829,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"}],"chapter":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir","Chapter At-Takwir","Takwir","Surah Takwir","Chapter Takwir","At Takwir","Surah At Takwir","Chapter At Takwir","Surah 81","Chapter 81","The Overthrowing","التكوير"]}